# Responsive Overhaul and CSS Layout Enhancements

This plan outlines the layout modifications and CSS adjustments to make the entire LalaKirana web application fully responsive, ensuring optimal visual styling, accessibility, and form functionality on small mobile devices (viewport widths <= 768px and <= 480px).

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> All changes are purely styling and responsiveness optimizations utilizing CSS Modules. No API endpoints or data structures are modified. All existing tests will continue to pass.

## Proposed Changes

We will systematically review and modify CSS Modules and corresponding components across the application layout and features:

---

### 1. Global Layout & Header

#### [MODIFY] [Header.module.css](file:///c:/MANAS/Projects/LK/Implementation/frontend/src/shared/layout/Header.module.css)
* Add subtle header title font-size scaling at different viewport widths to prevent text wrapping.
* Keep the left flex container clean and proportional on small screens.

