## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
* Build the application: `npm run build` in the `frontend` folder to guarantee clean compilation.
* Execute backend integration tests: `npm run test` in `backend` (Vitest).
* Execute frontend E2E tests: `npx playwright test` in `frontend` to verify nothing is broken.

### Manual Verification
* Run the dev server and use the browser agent to check layout visual outputs on multiple responsive dimensions:
  * Mobile view (375px wide)
  * Tablet view (768px wide)
  * Large screen view (1200px wide)
